trans-unit.source: Provides the definition of a custom SharePoint project item type.
trans-unit.target: 提供自定义 SharePoint 项目项类型的定义。

trans-unit.source: Implement the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeProvider> interface to define a custom type of SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 实现<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeProvider>接口可定义自定义 SharePoint 项目项类型。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Defining Custom SharePoint Project Item Types](/visualstudio/sharepoint/defining-custom-sharepoint-project-item-types.md) and [How to: Define a SharePoint Project Item Type](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-define-a-sharepoint-project-item-type.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[定义自定义 SharePoint 项目项类型](/visualstudio/sharepoint/defining-custom-sharepoint-project-item-types.md)和[如何： 定义 SharePoint 项目项类型](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-define-a-sharepoint-project-item-type.md)。

trans-unit.source: Classes that implement this interface must include the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportAttribute?displayProperty=fullName> and the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointProjectItemTypeAttribute> to be discovered by the project system.
trans-unit.target: 实现此接口的类必须包括<xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportAttribute?displayProperty=fullName>和<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointProjectItemTypeAttribute>项目系统发现。

trans-unit.source: A project item type definition to initialize.
trans-unit.target: 要初始化的项目项类型定义。

trans-unit.source: Called by projects to initialize an instance of a SharePoint project item type.
trans-unit.target: 由项目调用，用于初始化 SharePoint 项目项类型的实例。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemType> instance will be frozen after this method call which means that its properties cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemType>实例将被冻结之后此方法调用，这意味着不更改其属性。
